00:13:36.950 --> 00:13:38.620
Buradan asansörle çıkamayız.

00:13:38.620 --> 00:13:39.750
Asansör mesele değil.

00:13:42.580 --> 00:13:43.700
Wang Ağabey,

00:13:43.700 --> 00:13:45.580
